        <abstract>
            <p>CD accepts membership in the Birmingham Natural History Society.</p>
            <p>Thanks RLT for article. CD cannot quite agree that "under a theological point of view, the origin of evil is explained by survival".</p>
            <p>Is glad RLT has not given up polydactylism.</p>
        </abstract>
